sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户(MetaMask/EOA)
    participant FE as 前端(Next.js)
    participant BE as 后端(Go)
    participant B as Bundler(Alchemy)
    participant EP as EntryPoint
    participant A as 7702账户逻辑(DelegateAccount)
    participant PM as Paymaster
    participant T as MockUSDT

    U->>FE: 连接钱包 + 签Permit + 签UserOp
    FE->>BE: 请求quote/sponsor并提交userOp
    BE->>B: eth_sendUserOperation(UserOp, EntryPoint)

    B->>EP: 上链handleOps(外层tx.from=Bundler)
    EP->>A: validateUserOp(userOpHash, signature)
    A-->>EP: 验签结果

    EP->>PM: validatePaymasterUserOp(...)
    PM-->>EP: context + validationData

    EP->>A: 执行userOp.callData
    A->>T: transfer(收款地址, 金额)

    EP->>PM: postOp(actualGasCost, context)
    PM->>T: permit(user -> paymaster)
    PM->>T: transferFrom(user -> paymaster, gas token)

    EP->>B: 给beneficiary结算BNB
